        "title": {
          "english": "Formal Greeting: As-salamu alaykum",
          "arabic": "تحية رسمية: السلام عليكم"
        },
        "text": "This is a common, respectful, and widely used Islamic greeting that translates to 'Peace be upon you.' It's suitable for almost any situation and any time of day.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "السلام عليكم.",
            "english": "Hello / Peace be upon you.",
            "transliteration": "As-salamu alaykum."
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Responding to As-salamu alaykum",
          "arabic": "الرد على السلام عليكم"
        },
        "text": "The standard and polite response to 'As-salamu alaykum' is 'Wa alaykum as-salam,' meaning 'And upon you be peace.'",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "وعليكم السلام.",
            "english": "And upon you be peace.",
            "transliteration": "Wa alaykum as-salam."
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
