          "english": "Informal Greeting: Ahlan",
          "arabic": "تحية غير رسمية: أهلاً"
        },
        "text": "'Ahlan' is a friendly and informal way to say 'hello' or 'welcome' in Egyptian Arabic. It's often used with friends, family, or people you know well.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "أهلاً.",
            "english": "Hello / Welcome.",
            "transliteration": "Ahlan."
          }
        ]
      }
